import {Container,Avatar, Button, Grid, Paper, Typography, TextField } from "@mui/material"
import LockIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Lock';
import useStyles from "./styles"
function Auth(){
    const classes = useStyles();
    const isSignUp = true;

    function handleSubmit(){

    }

    function handleChange(){

    }

    return(
        <Container component='main' maxWidth="xs">
            <Paper className={classes.paper} elevation={3}>
                <Avatar className={classes.avatar}>
                    <LockIcon />
                </Avatar>
                <Typography variant='h5'>{isSignUp ? 'Sign Up': 'Sign In'}</Typography>
                <form className={classes.form} onSubmit={handleSubmit}>
                    <Grid container spacing={2}>
                        {
                            isSignUp && (
                                <>
                                    <Grid xs={6} md={12}>
                                        <TextField name='firstName' label='First Name' handleChange={handleChange} autoFocus xs={6} variant='outlined'/>
                                    </Grid>
                                    <Grid xs={6} md={12}>
                                        <TextField name='lastName' label='Last Name' handleChange={handleChange} autoFocus xs={6} variant='outlined'/>
                                    </Grid>
                                    <Grid xs={6} md={12}>
                                        <TextField type="tel" name='phone' label='Phone number' handleChange={handleChange} autoFocus xs={6} variant='outlined'/>
                                    </Grid>
                                    <Grid xs={6} md={12}>
                                        <TextField type="text" name='adress' label='Address' handleChange={handleChange} autoFocus xs={6} variant='outlined'/>
                                    </Grid>
                                </>
                            )}
                            <Grid xs={6} md={12}>
                                <TextField type="email" name='email' label='Email' handleChange={handleChange} autoFocus xs={6} variant='outlined'/>
                            </Grid>
                            <Grid xs={6} md={12}>
                                <TextField type='password' name='password'label='Password' handleChange={handleChange} autoFocus xs={6} variant='outlined'/>
                            </Grid>
                            {isSignUp && 
                            <Grid xs={6} md={12}>
                                <TextField type='password' name="confirmPassword"label='Confirm Password' handleChange={handleChange} autoFocus xs={6} variant='outlined'/>
                            </Grid>
                            }
                    </Grid>
                    <Button type="submit" fullWidth variane="contained" color="primary">{isSignUp ? "Sign Up" : "Sign In"}</Button>
                </form>
            </Paper>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default Auth;
